annotationA: Aminomethyltransferase; The glycine cleavage system catalyzes the degradation of glycine; Belongs to the GcvT family
annotationB: 10-formyltetrahydrofolate dehydrogenase; Hydroxymethyl-, formyl- and related transferase activity; methyltransferase activity; formyltetrahydrofolate dehydrogenase activity; oxidoreductase activity, acting on the aldehyde or oxo group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor.
